_______________________________________________________________________________
"Probe"       
        This allows the psionicist to invade a monster's mind for any
        useful experiences or information it contains.  The monster is
        left permanently mentally scarred.  It works once per monster,
        lowering the monster's experience and raising the psionicist's
        experience.  You will gain less experience when killing a monster
        that has been probed, but the great advantage is being able to
        learn something without having to kill the target first.  The cost
        of a probe depends on how tough the opponent is you are trying to
        probe.
 
SP Cost:  Variable	Guild Level:  8	Potential Points:  4
 
Command:  probe <target>
